{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"我们能顶半边天","authors":["于芳","周克周"],"dates":[{"year":1975,"month":3,"day":8}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们能顶半边天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小靳庄大队妇代会主任　周克周"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产队妇女队长　于　芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银云飘飘星星闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮明月空中悬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政治夜校灯光亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得社员心里暖。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动妇女打头炮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"批判会上先发言。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"提起林彪孔老二，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔怒火胸中燃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔孟之道横行霸道几千年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动妇女挣扎在无底深渊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孔老二胡说“唯女子与小人为"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难养也”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯恐妇女和奴隶闹翻天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"林彪也跟着孔老二，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诬蔑咱们只知道柴米和油盐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党领导人民闹革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动妇女有了发言权。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席信任咱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把劳动妇女比作半边天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代不同了，男女都一样，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男同志办到的，女同志也能办。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级敌人恨入骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千方百计阻挡妇女往前干，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡诌什么“驴驾辕，马拉套，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老娘们当家瞎胡闹”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诬蔑妇女“头发长；见识短”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们针锋相对作斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定要把社会主义事业扛在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世上绝无天生智，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知识才干靠实践。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依靠群众威力大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗天斗地斗敌顽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时代不同今胜昔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女能顶半边天。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}